<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>Use this page to detail your site's privacy policy.</p>

<h2>Information We Collect</h2>
<p>
  Describe the types of information you collect from users and how it is
  collected.
</p>

<h2>How We Use Collected Information</h2>
<p>Explain how the collected information is used and for what purposes.</p>

<h2>Information Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
<p>Specify if and how you share user information with third parties.</p>

<h2>Data Security</h2>
<p>
  Outline the measures you take to protect user data and ensure its security.
</p>

<h2>Third-Party Links</h2>
<p>
  Explain if there are any external links on your website and how they are
  handled.
</p>

<h2>Changes to this Privacy Policy</h2>
<p>State how and when you may update or modify the privacy policy.</p>

<h2>Contact Us</h2>
<p>
  Provide contact information for users to reach out with privacy-related
  concerns.
</p>

